OL,3,CVeteran forced to raid pension for
OL,4,Clifesaving heart surgery
OL,6,FITV News Political Correspondent Lise
OL,7,FMcNally spoke to Neil Wogan about his
OL,8,Fwait for a cardiologist.
OL,10,FA Royal Navy veteran says he felt
OL,11,F'forced' into paying thousands for
OL,12,Flife-saving surgery after being told
OL,13,Fhe faced months on the NHS waiting
OL,14,Flist.
OL,16,FNeil Wogan, 52, from Greater
OL,17,FManchester, spent the summer of 2023
OL,18,Fliving with a time bomb - one that was
OL,19,Fticking away in his chest. After being
OL,20,Frushed to A&E in Wigan he was told he
OL,21,Fhad a failing heart valve.
