OL,3,CVeteran forced to raid pension for
OL,4,Clifesaving heart surgery
OL,6,FNeil said: "I was very poorly. The
OL,7,Fcolour was leaving me, my breathing
OL,8,Fwas very shallow at the time, I knew I
OL,9,Fneeded that surgery, sooner rather
OL,10,Fthan later."
OL,12,FAfter waiting four months to see a
OL,13,Fcardiologist - Neil learnt it would be
OL,14,Fat least another four month wait for
OL,15,Fthe life saving surgery due to the
OL,16,Fsize of the heart care waiting list on
OL,17,Fthe NHS.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
