OL,4,Clifesaving heart surgery
OL,6,FThere are more than 400,000 people
OL,7,Fcurrently on the waiting list for
OL,8,Fcardiovascular care and around 40% of
OL,9,Fthem are waiting longer than the NHS's
OL,10,F18 week target.
OL,12,FThe British Heart Foundation says its
OL,13,Fa cardiovascular crisis and is urging
OL,14,Fthe Government to come up with a
OL,15,FNational Plan to tackle it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
