OL,3,CVeteran forced to raid pension for
OL,4,Clifesaving heart surgery
OL,6,FDr Sonya Babu-Narayan, Clinical
OL,7,FDirector at the British Heart
OL,8,FFoundation said: "People often hear
OL,9,Fabout NHS numbers, and hear the word
OL,10,F'18 weeks', but when it comes to your
OL,11,Fheart you can't wait. It's not a
OL,12,Fluxury to have heart surgery-you could
OL,13,Fdie if you aren't treated in time."
OL,15,FIn response the Government said
OL,16,Fcurrent waiting times were "completely
OL,17,Funacceptable".
