OL,4,Clifesaving heart surgery
OL,6,FIn a statement they added: "We are
OL,7,Fdetermined to end the two-tier
OL,8,Fhealthcare system where people are
OL,9,Fforced to pay to be seen on time,
OL,10,Fwhile those who can't afford it are
OL,11,Fleft behind.
OL,13,F"In the past seven months, we have
OL,14,Fended the strikes, delivered the extra
OL,15,Ftwo million appointments we promised,
OL,16,Fand have cut waiting lists by 160,000.
OL,17,FThere's a long way to go but the NHS
OL,18,Fis finally on the road to recovery."
